地嘅幻想<br />\nH類出路望落易搵工過U類 完全係幻覺<br />\n只係因為讀H類既多數有 EU passport / 直程係local Dutch...<br />\nU類讀完master 都好難搵工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />何況h類<br />\n即使local 好多都係讀完h類再pre master 上u類冼底<br />\n但大公司請人會偏好直升既 (Vwo -&gt; WO 多過 HBO上)<br />\n<br />\n利申讀緊master <br />\n淨係熟finance related job field"},{"pid":"354f331b24efe36f69e286fe6fa2d91b8a6c4d9f","tid":2259014,"uid":355065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b98be41b5134c3004027239736919d16e6cb8768","tid":2259014,"uid":16858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:58:42.000Z","msg":"有無人而家係歐洲/荷蘭？想問下實際疫情情況係點樣？<br />\n<br />\n可以照常出街嗎？ 因為想起行去果邊搵工，但又擔心疫情嚴重，始終歐洲又有新一波疫情。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有人而家係果邊住緊嗎？情況如何？如果而家起程過去安全嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T20:45:58.000Z","msg":"人在捷克 爆左好耐<br />\n9月開始第二度在家工作<br />\n睇黎今年都唔洗再返去<br />\n日日15000單 只比超市 外賣開門<br />\n緊急狀態左一排<br />\n既上9點後唔比出街<br />\n悶到嘔"},{"pid":"4c6f5269417e304677db7b0908feaf3ed4424032","tid":2259014,"uid":122826,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01626670c8f1824d0b2aa036e7aa97c268b93a93","tid":2259014,"uid":305696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d8156501b073bbe613e0b9d6506c499ebd296ce","tid":2259014,"uid":307982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3f34199be79053492889dbd50d1a05aab6ac4ef","tid":2259014,"uid":305696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T20:47:44.000Z","msg":"Pass曬所有科可以轉入u類<br />\n我一開始都係膽博膽 foundation -&gt; U類<br />\nDse best 5 得15分 仲要做左幾年野先去荷蘭<br />\n夠勤力就pick up到 <br />\nbachelor year 1 全5.5 or 6 追到 Year 3 尾果個sem 全9<br />\n而家入左RSM finance master 第一個block 都係9<br />\n同時係ING 做緊full time intern (Coverage role)<br />\n遲下會轉去ABNAmro 做sustainable finance coverage"},{"pid":"8bc8c93f427fd7f38fb976de52f09a056e3b1610","tid":2259014,"uid":198539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"571c01a59cf999dca690bfdc14a4d7913fdd3fde","tid":2259014,"uid":103146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f404a4ed21362d22f02b4ab87217fcf77dab83d9","tid":2259014,"uid":16858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b759fe46fa7a88b1e07edda4703a5045c8fa328","tid":2259014,"uid":103146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人在歐洲<br />\n室內地方同公共交通工具會戴口罩，我呢邊未封城所以重出得街<br />\n<br />\n疫情期間搵工難，而且見工都應該係用skype/MS Team/Zoom，你會唔會考慮下喺香港send 住cv先？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"唔該哂巴打！你係邊區？我一直都有sd啊，一直係香港都有份工。<br />\n本身想9月過去master, 但呢排份牛工太大壓力，想quit左提早過去settle 哂先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:17:27.000Z","msg":"德國<br />\n我都係讀緊master，留意返非歐盟居民可能要早半年到申請。有部分課程會少咗人爭易入啲。<br />\n另外德國本地同領事館出簽證速度都好慢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T00:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de756cf26a9a155032bdd1b982428f9f4e3358c","tid":2259014,"uid":103146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bc8c93f427fd7f38fb976de52f09a056e3b1610","tid":2259014,"uid":198539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"571c01a59cf999dca690bfdc14a4d7913fdd3fde","tid":2259014,"uid":103146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f404a4ed21362d22f02b4ab87217fcf77dab83d9","tid":2259014,"uid":16858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"唔該哂巴打！你係邊區？我一直都有sd啊，一直係香港都有份工。<br />\n本身想9月過去master, 但呢排份牛工太大壓力，想quit左提早過去settle 哂先"},"citedBy":1,"replyT